data.description:
Ranch Style Rambler, 2,200 sq Ft Waterfront Home , 15,000 sq ft Lo twith detached 2 Car Garage and shop insulated with heat and A/C. Bonus Room/Office and laundry room with counters and sink. 3 Seperate patios. Fully Fenced with Gardens, Fruit trees and Lawn.
Complete remodel new Master Bath and full Chefs Kitchen 2022
data.whatILove:
Waterfront Double Lot. Remodeled 2022. Spectacular Views of Lake and Mountains. Steps away from Walking trail and 100 feet away from Priest Rapids Lake front Beach.
Detached 2 Car garage. 3 Separate patio areas. Fully fenced, Gardens, fruit trees & Lawn.
